channel.title: Comments on: Is Torosaurus Triceratops? The debate rages on!

item.title: By: Jaime A. Headden
item.dc:creator: Jaime A. Headden
item.description:
In reply to <a href="http://fossilsandshit.com/is-torosaurus-triceratops-the-debate-rages-on/#comment-434">protohedgehog</a>.
Science gives us reasons to science, like a perpetual science machine ... of science. Why, the very thought of doing science makes me want to do science. Where's an hypothesis I can test!?1
